@NODE int "Introduction"

Hello
-----
Welcome to the Footy Game, by Matthew Briggs, ENGiNE NiNE DESiGN 1998. Basically, its a `football spectator' program which allows you to type in two team names and six striker names (three on each team), and then after clicking `play' watch, your teams play a game of footy. This is not the best of programs, but it does entertain for a few minutes.

@ENDNODE

@NODE requ "System Requirements"

Requirements
