* An assignment locating TheFootyGame:

@ENDNODE


@NODE game "How to play the game"

The Main Menu
-------------
In the main menu, you must type or select two teams, if you do not, the `play' gadget will not work. Clicking on `Team A' or `Team B' will automatically give you a team from the premier league. Please note that the some of the default teams may be out-dated or inaccurate.

The Game
--------
The game lasts for 90 seconds, split into two halves, plus pauses for the text commentary. If a player gets sent off, or injured then that team has less chance of scoring a goal. No skill is involved whilst playing, as the game is totally random.

@ENDNODE

